properties.text: Our journey starts deep in the benthic abyss. We now must find a way to the surface of the sea and reach the volcano. Best to tread carefully as devious traps and deadly life forms inhabit these waters.
A Blocker Fish! Maybe if we had some dynamite...

We’ve met the guardian of the abyss, a mermaid with a diamond fetish. At least she won’t kill us, yet. But she will only activate the portal if we pay her an amount of 75 diamonds!
"Thank you, good traveller. I have activated the portal into the valley of madness. Oh, and one more thing. I will take care of your surplus of diamonds, too!"
